						<div class="postbody">Tools that I use all the time: HxD as a good hex editor, Notepad++ as a code editor, Graphics Gale and GIMP as general purpose graphics editors, NES Screen Tool as a NES graphics editor.<br /><br />There are no special tools to create a blank NES ROM, as it is not something that has any practical use.</div>

